OL,3,COfficer won't face charges following
OL,4,Cteenagers' deaths which sparked riots
OL,6,FTensions between local people and
OL,7,Fpolice at the scene led to a riot
OL,8,Flasting several hours, during which
OL,9,Ftime dozens of officers were injured,
OL,10,Fproperty was damaged and cars were set
OL,11,Falight.
OL,13,FPreviously, the Independent Office for
OL,14,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) said the driver
OL,15,Fof the police van had been told they
OL,16,Fwere being criminally investigated for
OL,17,Fdangerous driving after being served
OL,18,Fwith a gross misconduct notice.
