OL,6,F"Following a thorough and detailed
OL,7,Freview of the evidence in relation to
OL,8,Fa single allegation of dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving in this case, we have decided
OL,10,Fthat no criminal charges will be
OL,11,Fbrought against a South Wales Police
OL,12,Fofficer.
OL,14,F"We have concluded that there is
OL,15,Finsufficient evidence to provide a
OL,16,Frealistic prospect of conviction.
