OL,6,F"We fully understand that this will be
OL,7,Fdisappointing news for the families of
OL,8,Fboth boys and will offer a meeting
OL,9,Fwith them to explain our reasoning
OL,10,Ffurther."
OL,12,FThe IOPC said it submitted a file of
OL,13,Fevidence to the CPS to consider an
OL,14,Foffence of dangerous driving for the
OL,15,Fdriver of a police van.
