OL,6,FNoting today's decision by the CPS,
OL,7,Fthe IOPC director David Ford said: "We
OL,8,Fare finalising our position over any
OL,9,Fpotential disciplinary proceedings in
OL,10,Frelation to the driver of the police
OL,11,Fvan and will provide a further update
OL,12,Fonce final decisions have been made."
OL,14,FThe watchdog said an additional
OL,15,Finvestigation into family complaints
OL,16,Fagainst South Wales Police, which
OL,17,Fcovered a number of areas including
OL,18,Fthe families' treatment at the scene
OL,19,Fof the incident, is close to
OL,20,Fconcluding.
